@node "Changes" "THOR.guide/Changes"
@next "Index"
@prev "Thanks"
@toc "Main"

Changes to this documentation
*****************************

This  section  lists changes that have been made to this documentation
during  the  last  few  THOR releases.  It is not a list of changes to
THOR itself, see the THOR.history file for these.

@{b}Changes in this doc for THOR 2.2:@{ub}
     - Added a separate chapter on how to repair the message database
     should this be needed. See @{"Repairing a damaged database" link "Repairing a damaged database"}.

     - Updated the docs on the information shown in the userdatabase
     main  window. See @{"User database" link "User database"}.

     - Updated to docs on the menus to include the new options.  See
     @{"Menus" link "Menus"}.

     - Updated to docs on the @{"Group by" link "Group by"} option to include the new
     Subject+Thread group method.

     - Updated the docs on @{"Join" link "Join"} conference.

     - Updated the docs on the @{"Messagelist Window" link "Messagelist Window"} to include
     information about the new multiselection feature.

     - Added docs on the new options in the @{"Reply" link "Reply"} and Enter message
     window.

     - Added docs on the maintenance option in the kill/emphasize
     database.  See @{"Kill database" link "Kill database"}.

     - Added docs on the new @{"WatchTHOR" link "WatchTHOR"} program.

     - Added docs on the new shortcut for turning on/off the extra
     header   fields. See @{"Shortcuts" link "Shortcuts"}.

     - Added docs on the SHIFT-ESC shortcut combination.  See
     @{"Shortcuts" link "Shortcuts"}.

     - Added docs on the 2 new @{"Group by" link "Group by"} modes Subject Alpha and
     Subject+Thread Alpha.

     - Added docs on the new options in the newsbrowser in ConnectTHOR.
     See @{"ConnectTHOR" link "ConnectTHOR"}.

     - The Show Headers and Show Styles buttons present in the mail
     window is documented in @{"Message header" link "Message header"}.

     - The various MIME decoding/encoding methods supported is
     documented in the @{"MIME support" link "MIME support"} section.

@{b}Changes in this doc for THOR 2.3:@{ub}
     - Kjell and Magne updated the MIME section and the about section.

     - Added the keypad shortcuts to the @{"Shortcuts" link "Shortcuts"} section.

     - Updated the @{"Group by" link "Group by"} section.

     -  Updated  the  docs on Style Tags in the @{"Visual Options Window" link "Visual Options Window"}
     section.

     - Updated the docs on the @{"Messagelist Window" link "Messagelist Window"} to describe the new
     gadget.

     -  Updated  the ConfigTHOR.guide in the reply string section and
     added the 2 new forward codes.

     -  Updated  the  @{"Mark Window" link "Mark Window"}  on the new "mark login conference"
     function.

     - Added the new Catchup Upto to the @{"Menus" link "Menus"} session.

     - Did not find a place for the env variable
     "THOR/SYSTEM_ENTRY_CONFLIST" in the docs, read THOR.history for
     more info about it.

     -  Added  docs  on "Auto Show First Message", "Delayed Msg Unmark"
     and the   new   external   editor   command   line   formatting
     code  in ConfigTHOR.guide.

     - Added docs on the new @{"Pack-Purge Window" link "Pack-Purge Window"}.

     -   Updated   the   docs   on   the  @{"CfgTCP" link "CfgTCP"},  @{"ConnectTHOR" link "ConnectTHOR"},
     @{"SendTCP" link "SendTCP"} and @{"GetTCP" link "GetTCP"} programs.

     - Updated the docs for THOR 2.4.

@{b}Changes in this doc for THOR 2.5:@{ub}
     - Added docs on the changes in @{"Pack-Purge Window" link "Pack-Purge Window"}.

     - Added docs on the changes in the @{"Kill database" link "Kill database"}, including   a
     few tips and clarifications.

     - Updated @{"MIME support" link "MIME support"} to include information about external
     icons.

     - Added information about double-clicking on names in the
     @{"User database" link "User database"}.

     - Updated the @{"ConnectTHOR" link "ConnectTHOR"} documentation to include the 2 new
     arguments   and the new "Filter crosspostings" option in the
     browser.

     - Updated the @{"Group by" link "Group by"} section to include info that it can be used
      even in All and Search mode now.

     - Updated the @{"Visual Options Window" link "Visual Options Window"} documentation with the new
     link features   along with the option to show pictures
     automatically.

     - Updated the documentation on the forward code for first and last
     name, that   was implemented some time ago but never documented.
     See @{"Import/Export options" link "ConfigTHOR.guide/Import-Export"}.

@{b}Changes in this doc for THOR 2.6:@{ub}
     - Added a section on @{"Mail Transport" link "Mail Transport"} which explains how mail is
     sent and   received using the SMTP and POP3 protocols.

     - Added FilterThor in the @{"Menus" link "Menus"} section.

     - Updated the documentation on the @{"Conference Window" link "Conference Window"} for the new
     layout   and organization of the window.

     - Added documentation on the new @{"Save-Print Window" link "Save-Print Window"} that was added
     for   Thor 2.6.


@endnode

